quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  21,11,"Heewii ko Min kalki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko too√Īunde Min pu…ó…ói …ďaawo mayre yim…ďe goo."
  21,12,"Tuma nde …ďe so'unoo Lepte amen …óen, tawi kam…ďe he…ďe ndoga …óe."
  21,13,"Wota on ndogu, nduttee fa'ade e ko neemina…óon kon e mu'un e ko…óan…óe mo'on, mbelejo'o on lannditoyte."
  21,14,"∆Āe mbi'a: "Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, minen min laatinoke too√Ī…ďe"."
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu ma…ď…ďe, haa Men mba…óa …ďe co√Īateeri ko …ďe may…ďe."
  21,16,"Min tagaani kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Min fijoo…ďe."
  21,17,"Sinndo Min 'a'andino nde Min njogotoo fijindaaru, Min njogitotono …óum immorde ka Amen si tawii Min laatike wa…óoo…ďe."
  21,18,"Ko woni, Mi…óen mberloo Goonga ka e dow mehre nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko cifoto…óon."
  21,19,"Ko KaŇčko woodani ko woni ko ka kammuuji e ka leydi …ďen won…ďe ka Makko kadi …ďe mawnittaako ga rewugol Mo, …ďe hasrintaaka kadi."
  21,20,"He…ďe cubhinoo jemma e √Īaloma …ďe ngaamataa."
  21,21,"Kaa …ďe njogiti dewetee…ói ka leydi kannji hi…ói immintina [may…ďe …ďen]."
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli …ói e leydi ndi] dewetee…ói ko wonaa Alla …ói bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin ga ko…ďe cifotoo."
  21,23,"O la…ďndetaake ko o gollata ko, kam…ďe ko …ďe la…ďnditoytee…ďe."
  21,24,"Kaa …ďe njogiti gaanin makko dewetee…ói? Maaki: "ngaddee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni jaŇčta …ďe won'…óu…ďe e am e jaŇčta …ďen adii…ďe kam". Ko woni, …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe …ďe anndaa Goonga kan kam…ďe ko …ďe …óurnii…ďe."